hasNutrient some @E*, hasNutrient some @F*, hasNutrient some @G*, hasNutrient some @H*

Class: @B*
SubClassOf: hasShape some @AW*, hasShape some @AX*, hasShape some @AY*

Class: @B*

Class: @B*
SubClassOf: hasFlavor some @G*, hasFlavor some @I*, hasFlavor some @J*

Class: @B*
SubClassOf: canCook some @AM*, canCook some @AN*, canCook some @AO*,
canCook some @AP*, canCook some @AQ*, canCook some @AR*

Class: @A*

hasMineral some @L*, hasMineral some @M*, hasMineral some @N*, hasMineral some @O*,
hasMineral some @P*, hasMineral some @Q*

Class: @B*
SubClassOf: hasTexture some @AZ*, hasTexture some @BA*, hasTexture some @BC*

Class: @A*
SubClassOf: hasVitamin some @R*, hasVitamin some @S*, hasVitamin some @T*, 
hasVitamin some @U*, hasVitamin some @V*, hasVitamin some @W*, 
hasVitamin some @X*, hasVitamin some @Y*, hasSugar some @Z*
